         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility"> ¶ Hamburg, 22 May 1854 ¶ Most ¶  ¶ esteemed ¶  ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ Yesterday I received your package, and already today I come with a request. In the ¶  ¶ Flora berolinensis ¶  ¶ you have mentioned ¶  ¶ Zann...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M54.05.22</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Wilhelm Sonder to Diederich von Schlechtendal</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS not seen; text given here is extracted from Tkach, Neubauer &amp; Roser (2022), Brief 21.</p>
               </note>Hamburg d. 22 Mai 54</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Geehrtester Herr,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gestern empfing ich Ihr Packet, und schon heute komme ich mit einer Bitte. Sie haben in der Flor. berolinen. Zannichellia mit sehr langen Staubfäden u 4-fächrigen Antheren erwähnt, die in Westphalen vorkommen soll. Ist es Ihnen nicht möglich, mir ein Bruchstück dieser Pflanze in einem Briefe mitzutheilein? Es wäre mir der Vergleichung wegen von grosser Wichtigkeit. Es wird ohne Zweifel die von Gay Zannichell. macrostemon genannte Art sein, die ich auch zu besitzen glaube, doch sind meine Exemplare nicht der Art, um mit Sicherheit ein Urtheil darüber zu haben. Durch umgehende Uebersendung eines Fragmentes würden Sie mich sehr erfreuen.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In ca. 8 Tagen gedenk ich Ihnen das Manuskript der Müller’schen Proteaceen zuzustellen, das mir Prof. Meisner so eben übersendet; leider hat er aber nicht die Standörter beigefügt, so wie es sein sollte, u. dazu muss ich erst die Sammlung durchsehen. Miquel arbeitet jetzt auch mit.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Hochachtungsvoll</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>ergebenster<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hamburg, 22 May 1854</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Most<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>esteemed<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yesterday I received your package, and already today I come with a request. In the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Flora berolinensis</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>you have mentioned<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Zannichellia</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>with very long stamens and 4-fold anthers, which is said to occur in Westphalia. Is it not possible for you to send me a fragment of this plant in a letter? It would be of great importance to me for the sake of comparison. It will undoubtedly be the species<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>called<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by Gay<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Zannichell</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">ia</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>macrostemon</seg>, which I also believe to be in possession of, but my specimens are not of the kind to enable me to judge for certain. I would be very pleased if you would send me a fragment<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>at your earliest convenience.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In about 8 days I intend to send you the manuscript of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Mueller<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Proteaceae, which Prof. Meisner has just sent me; unfortunately, however, he has not added the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>localities<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>as he should have, and for them<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I must first look through the collection. Miquel is now also collaborating.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>most<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>devoted</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
